        Instantiates a new door.
        Parameters:
        name - the name
        radius - the radius
        color - the color
        interiorZone - the interior zone of action inside a layer
        exteriorZone - the exterior zone of action outside a layer
        toInputZone - the to input zone to get molecules
        toOutputZone - the to output zone to put molecules
        type - the type of the door symporter, antiporter, etc.
        moleculeInputs - the list of molecule to get with input door
        moleculeOutputs - the list of molecule to get with input door
        cellInteriorRadius - the radius of action inside the cell
        cellExteriorRadius - the radius of action outside the cell
        id - the unique id that the door determines unequivocally
